node.text:
I feel like WE have been grieving all year. 2020 has been REAL, to say the least. God has been taking everyone home expeditiously. This year has taken a toll on everyone, literally. 

Idk about you but I am emotionally DRAINED. From the pandemic, politics, police brutality, and death looking us right in our faces on a daily basis. Im tired. 

Check on your family and friends please. Don’t take their silence as disrespect. We are all going through a lot right now. Yes the phone works two ways but pick it up if you’re thinking about someone you love or care about. Life is too damn short... 

#grief #pandemic2020 #mourning #death  #love #lifeisshort
